  <div class="p-box-text">
    <p class="text-alt-small-left">Designing the way the work is showed and the space around it is just as important as the project itself. A modern black & white theme may look the most professional, but it doesn't speak to the kind of designer I am.</p>
    <p class="text-alt-small-left">I love color, tactility, and retro-futuristic design--whether that be a physical product, graphic, or game. I chose to design my website to reflect this playfulness, while keeping it simple and letting the projects speak for themselves.</p>
