    <p class="text-small">Development</p>
    <p class="text-alt-small-left">This website is hand-coded using HTML, CSS, and Javascript. I used Eleventy, a static site generator, to write layouts and reuse them across my pages automatically. So if I want to update my header or sidebar, I don't have to manually change the code on every page.</p>
    <p class="text-alt-small-left">I write the code in Visual Studio, push versions to Github using Windows Terminal, which automatically updates my website on Neocities. This fully automated process makes it easy to upload text and photos, and add new projects in minutes.</p>    
